beauty.name: PLUM Skin Revival Face Wash
beauty.description: Exposure to the sun can irritate the skin and also lead to free-radical damage that can cause age spots, pigmentation, wrinkles and much else. Soothing Chamomile, rejuvenating White Tea and antioxidant-rich botanical extracts: just perfect to relax, refresh and revive skin that's exposed to the sun and the elements. Soap-free, gentle foaming face wash that will make your skin smile!

beauty.name: LAKME Fairnes Face Wash
beauty.description: Cleanse your skin with Lakme Perfect radiance face wash to remove all the traces of dirt, pollution, sweat and oiliness from your skin. It deep cleans your skin right down to the pores to ensure a radiant looking skin.

accessories.description: A work of perfect craftmanship, this analog-digital watch is detailed with minute precision and comes with a sleek design, and will lend you a modish look.
